rows.name: Welcome welcoooooome! â™ª

rows.label: qst100406_msg0002
rows.name:
Mo-mo! It's friends from
before. Thank you for help.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0003
rows.name:
Now customers come from near
and far to hear Falala sing.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0004
rows.name:
But... It hard to become famous
everywhere just through good singing.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0005
rows.name:
News of Falala will never reach
sonnypon Solala at this rate.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0006
rows.name: Oh, but! Falala have idea!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0007
rows.name: Besides Falala's good singing...

rows.label: qst100406_msg0008
rows.name:
Falala will become famous
through delicious foods!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0009
rows.name:
This will be known as restaurant for
listen to Mom Falala's singing and
eat Mom Falala's yummy cooking.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0010
rows.name:
Solala will hear about it and
come to see his beloved Mom.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0011
rows.name:
No time to waste, Falala
must get cooking... Mo-mo?!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0012
rows.name:
Falala has run out of ingredients
to make her specialty dish!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0013
rows.name:
Cannot be made without Rhinon
Tail and Skwaror Rib-Eye Steak.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0014
rows.name:
Very rare for marketplace to stock
them... Please help, friends!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0015
rows.name:
Rhinon Tail is found in
Invidia, and Skwaror Rib-Eye
Steak is most common in Gula!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0101
rows.name:
Rhinon Tail come from
Nomad Rhinon in Invidia.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0102
rows.name:
Can get Skwaror Rib-Eye Steak
from Meldl Skwaror in Gula.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0103
rows.name:
If friends bring both, Falala
can make her famous stew!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0201
rows.name:
Did friends bring
ingredients for cooking?

rows.label: qst100406_msg0202
rows.name:
Thank you muchly! Falala will
start cooking right away!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0203
rows.name: Ta-da! It Spicy Stralu!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0204
rows.name:
When Solala had fever, or
when he wet bed, or when
he have girl trouble...

rows.label: qst100406_msg0205
rows.name:
His Mom always make this
for him! It have a lot of
special memories attached.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0206
rows.name:
Actually... Falala have one more
favor to ask of traveling friends.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0207
rows.name:
Falala has made flyers to
spread word of cooking!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0208
rows.name:
Please help stick flyers up on
notice boards in Central Exchange,
Torigo and Fons Maim.

rows.label: qst100406_msg0209
rows.name: Thank you! Good luck!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0210
rows.name:
Falala will make lots of
food to prepare for sudden
influx of customers!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0301
rows.name:
Please paste flyers on notice
boards in Central Exchange,
Torigo and Fons Maim!

rows.label: qst100406_msg0302
rows.name:
Come and let Falala
know when you finish!
